Rockville MD, 20851

To join the SneezyMUD listserver and find out about upcoming Sneezy events or
hear news and ideas from the gods before it happens, send an email to:
Maiser@LIB01.FERRIS.EDU
The Subject: line should be blank and the body of the email should contain
just the words: "sub sneezy"
